China.

33
00:01:31,850 --> 00:01:34,100
And they called for the EU to investigate.

34
00:01:34,100 --> 00:01:37,240
Well, to make sure this kind of embarrassing

35
00:01:37,240 --> 00:01:39,549
exposé of their human rights problems

36
