39
00:01:45,060 --> 00:01:47,399
To see if some players on team Europe

40
00:01:47,399 --> 00:01:51,509
could “accidentally” fumble the ball sometimes.

41
00:01:51,509 --> 00:01:52,600
Like Greece.

42
