an EU spokesperson said.

55
00:02:23,740 --> 00:02:25,550
Which is diplomat-speak for,

56
00:02:25,550 --> 00:02:28,390
“Hey Greece, that was not cool.”

57
00:02:28,390 --> 00:02:29,980
But China loved it.

58
00:02:29,980 --> 00:02:31,040
So much, in fact,

59
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:34,590
that it wants to buy a whole team of players
like Greece.

60
00:02:34,590 --> 00:02:38,470
It’s even got a name: 16 + 1.

61
00:02:38,470 --> 00:02:41,840
That is, 16 Central and Eastern European nations,

62
