63
00:02:45,580 --> 00:02:46,580
China!

64
00:02:46,580 --> 00:02:48,400
11 of those 16 countries

65
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:50,420
are on the field with the EU,

66
00:02:50,420 --> 00:02:52,500
