79
00:03:17,569 --> 00:03:20,260
Ah…the “tip of the iceberg.”

80
00:03:20,260 --> 00:03:21,319
Don’t worry.

81
00:03:21,319 --> 00:03:25,250
Icebergs are probably nothing to worry about.

82
00:03:25,250 --> 00:03:27,989
