In fact, since 2012,

98
00:04:04,650 --> 00:04:05,770
Chinese companies have announced

99
00:04:05,770 --> 00:04:08,739
15 billion dollars worth of investment.

100
00:04:08,739 --> 00:04:10,209
It’s now all being wrapped into

101
00:04:10,209 --> 00:04:12,610
China’s One Belt, One Road Initiative.

102
00:04:12,610 --> 00:04:14,280
And roads are getting built.

103
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:15,739
In 2014,

104
00:04:15,739 --> 00:04:17,780
Chinese state-owned power company and bank

105
