in Bosnia.

106
00:04:21,660 --> 00:04:24,410
And a year later, a different Chinese company

107
00:04:24,410 --> 00:04:26,870
signed a 3.6 billion dollar deal

108
00:04:26,870 --> 00:04:28,020
to build a highway between

109
00:04:28,020 --> 00:04:30,440
Albania and Montenegro.

110
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:32,970
These are glorious, heady times.

111
00:04:32,970 --> 00:04:34,600
