132
00:05:17,430 --> 00:05:20,050
Now that’s the team spirit!

133
00:05:20,050 --> 00:05:21,640
Knocking some of the teeth out of

134
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:24,070
Europe’s “one voice” policy on China

135
00:05:24,070 --> 00:05:25,660
is definitely part of the plan,

136
00:05:25,660 --> 00:05:26,900
say EU officials.

137
00:05:26,900 --> 00:05:29,710
“China’s strategy in Europe is divide
and rule,”

138
