an important EU initiative—

147
00:05:52,830 --> 00:05:54,680
that is, EU-wide screening

148
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:56,660
of foreign investments.

149
00:05:56,660 --> 00:06:00,669
The push for screenings comes as Chinese investment
skyrockets.

150
00:06:00,669 --> 00:06:01,669
Which also makes countries

151
