and less eager to criticize the Chinese regime.

153
00:06:07,090 --> 00:06:09,940
But “China’s lobbying has already proved
effective

154
00:06:09,940 --> 00:06:13,009
in diluting the proposed review process.”

155
00:06:13,009 --> 00:06:14,830
Basically, the screening process

156
00:06:14,830 --> 00:06:17,030
originally would have allowed the EU

157
00:06:17,030 --> 00:06:18,889
to block Chinese investments

158
00:06:18,889 --> 00:06:21,100
that threatened national security—

159
00:06:21,100 --> 00:06:23,340
like CFIUS does in the United States.

160
00:06:23,340 --> 00:06:25,090
But in the diluted version,

161
00:06:25,090 --> 00:06:27,669
it merely “allows EU institutions

162
00:06:27,669 --> 00:06:29,190
